24:34.474 --> 24:37.394
<i>Look both ways before you cross
the street, and don't forget:</i>

24:37.895 --> 24:41.648
<i>God is not real, but we respect
other people's belief systems.</i>

24:42.149 --> 24:44.985
<i>I'll be home for dinner. I love you. Mom.</i>

25:38.205 --> 25:41.166
