O gentle savior</i>

25:55.264 --> 25:59.268
<i>Hear my humble cry</i>

26:00.602 --> 26:05.566
<i>While on others thou art smiling</i>

26:06.066 --> 26:08.777
<i>Do not pass me by</i>

