because I don't know you.

26:31.884 --> 26:33.051
That makes sense.

26:34.887 --> 26:37.848
I'm Reverend Wakely. This is my church.

26:38.891 --> 26:43.020
I'm Mad Zott. I don't have a church
because my mom says God isn't real.

26:44.521 --> 26:45.689
I'm Linda's neighbor.

26:51.612 --> 26:54.198
A family tree. How fun.

26:55.199 --> 26:56.366
That's debatable.

26:57.451 --> 27:00.454
- Debatable?
- It means arguable.

27:02.122 --> 27:03.123
Yes, it does.

27:04.541 --> 27:05.709
What have you got so far?

27:08.212 --> 27:11.548
On my mom's side, I have Ezra and Iris,

27:11.548 --> 27:14.009
but I don't have anything
on my dad's side yet.

27:14.009 --> 27:15.427
I don't know where to start.

27:16.345 --> 27:17.638
Why not just ask him?

27:18.722 --> 27:19.932
He's dead.

27:21.892 --> 27:23.018
I'm so sorry.

27:24.102 --> 27:26.772
People say you can't miss
what you never had,

27:27.356 --> 27:30.692
but I think people are wrong. Don't you?

27:31.860 --> 27:34.238
I think people are very wrong.

27:35.822 --> 27:37.324
And what are these?

27:38.784 --> 27:41.119
Some clues I found in my dad's study,

27:41.703 --> 27:45.123
which I never went through,
if anyone ever asks you.

27:48.001 --> 27:52.548
