36:00.744 --> 36:04.623
I hope I'm not stepping on any toes,
but here's a list of all the St. Luke's

36:04.623 --> 36:10.045
in Alabama, Alaska, Arizona,
Arkansas, California, Colorado,

36:10.045 --> 36:11.964
Connecticut and Delaware.

36:11.964 --> 36:15.175
