the way to Wisconsin and Wyoming.

36:15.175 --> 36:18.136
Wow. How did you do this?

36:18.136 --> 36:20.264
I got them from the yellow pages
at the library.

36:20.764 --> 36:24.101
You go state by state and look up all
the St. Luke's. And there's a lot too.

36:24.601 --> 36:26.436
Churches tend not to have
the greatest imagination

36:26.436 --> 36:27.896
when it comes down to names.

36:27.896 --> 36:29.606
Why are you helping me?

36:30.107 --> 36:32.651
Because people who don't ask questions
have blind faith,

36:32.651 --> 36:35.737
and blind faith is the furthest thing
from faith.

36:37.281 --> 36:39.241
Can you say that again slower?

36:39.825 --> 36:41.869
"How would you describe the host?"

36:41.869 --> 36:47.791
"Stuck up." "Unpleasant."
"Didn't smile once."

36:48.375 --> 36:49.751
Smile?

36:49.751 --> 36:53.297
Do surgeons smile
while performing appendectomies? No.

36:53.297 --> 36:54.631
Would you want them to? No.

36:54.631 --> 36:56.592
- Mr. Lebensmal?
- Not now.

36:57.176 --> 37:00.304
If I tell you to smile,
you're gonna fucking smile.

37:00.304 --> 37:01.471
I will not.

37:01.471 --> 37:03.724
I think what Elizabeth is trying to say--

37:03.724 --> 37:05.601
He knows what I'm saying
because I'm saying it.

37:05.601 --> 37:07.144
Listen to me, young lady.

37:07.769 --> 37:10.981
I am the owner of this station.
Do you understand?

37:11.690 --> 37:14.860
Will someone answer those fucking phones?

37:16.612 --> 37:18.030
You cannot just come in here

37:18.030 --> 37:19.823
and do whatever the hell you want.

37:19.823 --> 37:23.952
I am not doing whatever the hell I want.
If I was, I would be in a research lab.

37:24.578 --> 37:25.787
Let me explain something to you.

37:25.787 --> 37:29.875
Men are always trying to explain,
and women are expected to sit and listen.

37:30.459 --> 37:32.169
I do not want this job,
but I need the money

37:32.169 --> 37:35.255
and I will work harder than anyone
to make this a show that I am proud of.

37:35.255 --> 37:38.592
But you want a show that perpetuates
the myth that women are imbeciles

37:38.592 --> 37:40.010
and the biggest decision of their day

37:40.010 --> 37:41.678
is what color
they're gonna paint their nails.

37:41.678 --> 37:44.973
I will not do that, and there is no amount
of menace that will change my mind.

37:44.973 --> 37:49.102
A man wants his wife to make him a drink
after a long day at work.

37:49.102 --> 37:52.231
So make the fucking drink.

37:52.231 --> 37:55.192
Why do you assume
that his day was longer than hers?

37:55.776 --> 37:57.528
Why don't you make the fucking drink?

37:57.528 --> 37:58.987
